HEALTH & MEDICAL DISCLAIMER

This software provides educational nutrition information only. It is NOT medical
advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult with qualified healthcare
professionals (registered dietitian, physician, or other appropriate provider)
before making significant dietary changes, especially if you have medical
conditions, are pregnant/nursing, or take medications.

If you are experiencing a medical emergency or mental health crisis, contact
emergency services or crisis hotlines immediately:

- United States: 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) or 911 (Emergency)
- National Eating Disorders Association: 1-800-931-2237
- International: Contact local emergency services

This disclaimer applies to all uses, modifications, and distributions of the
